    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, reflecting a consistent maintenance schedule. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. The interior is clean and comfortable, with all electronic features and climate control systems functioning properly. This is a dependable, honest car that is ready for its next owner without any immediate mechanical concerns.",
