    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been such a reliable companion for me and is still in wonderful shape, ready for plenty more adventures. It runs beautifully and has been well-loved and looked after. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s a joy to drive, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for you to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear torque through a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. Recent comprehensive service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle body actuators, ensuring the longevity of the 8,400 RPM valvetrain. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates for various road conditions. While the exterior finish shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the subframe and bushings are in excellent order, maintaining the precise turn-in and lateral stability this platform is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, accented by clean lines and only the minor, superficial blemishes consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a true sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of significant wear, while the dashboard and controls show no fading or mechanical fatigue. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the crisp infotainment system, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes and preventative maintenance. It drives tight, quiet, and confident, with no rattles or hesitations. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a high-quality, dependable vehicle that has been treated with genuine pride of ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously maintained, ensuring reliable performance and a refined driving experience. Offering a superb balance of luxury and utility, it stands as a testament to quality engineering and remains an exceptional choice for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34800.0,
